tab1.text1:
We hope you'll enjoy the server and mods.

When you spawn in, you will have engrams in your inventory that can be used to craft essentials. It only sticks around for 300 seconds and costs Fiber.

Get your free Argy, saddle, chitin armor, and metal tools from the Start Here beacons.

Rules:

1. No douchebaggery.

2. Don't build on spawn locations or prevent spawning.

3. Play well with others and have fun.

4. If you need help and an admin is not online, use Discord to leave a message.
